imdb.plot outline: Precious Cargo is a comedy about two tutors - sisters Lisa and Sandy - trying to help tiny one-percenters stay on top. Lisa and Sandy couldn't be more different. Lisa is a type A, super focused actor who takes her day job tutoring the children of Manhattan's elite very seriously. Sandy is a dreamer, a wanderer, with her hands in a bit of everything: pottery, sitar lessons, capoeira...every day, one passion flames out and a new one replaces it. When Lisa hooks Sandy up with a job at Tomorrow's Child of the Future tutoring company, she expects her to crash and burn. But the tables turn when Sandy is suddenly in high demand for her playful teaching methods, and Lisa's job is in jeopardy. When you're dealing with New York's persnickety rich and famous and their precious cargo, you never know how things will turn out.

When Lisa hooks Sandy up with a job at Tomorrow's Child of the Future tutoring company, she expects her to crash and burn.
